SQL_STMT_U.val:
select * from (select t.tr_indicatie as indication, t.tr_herkomst_code_tr as origincode, t.tr_mutatiecode as mutationcode, t.tr_mut_gemaakt as mutationmade, t.tr_transdatum as transactiondate, pmg.pmg_mutatie_aantal as amountbe, 0 as amountcl, case when t.tr_rel1 = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_rel1_rap_krs when t.tr_rel2 = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_rel2_rap_krs when t.tr_vruchtrelatie = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_vruchtrel_rap_krs else 1 end as clientquote, case when t.tr_rel1 = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_rel1_rap_fac when t.tr_rel2 = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_rel2_rap_fac when t.tr_vruchtrelatie = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_vruchtrel_rap_fac else 1 end as clientfactor, case when t.tr_rel1 = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_rel1_rap_rcp when t.tr_rel2 = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_rel2_rap_rcp when t.tr_vruchtrelatie = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_vruchtrel_rap_rcp else 1 end as clientreciproke, case when t.tr_rel1 = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_rel1_rek2_munts when t.tr_rel2 = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_rel2_rek2_munts when t.tr_vruchtrelatie = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_vruchtrek_muntsrt else 'XXX' end as clientaccountcurrency, case when t.tr_rel1 = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_rel1_munts_krs when t.tr_rel2 = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_rel2_munts_krs when t.tr_vruchtrelatie = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_vruchtrek_mnt_krs else 1 end as clientaccountquote, case when t.tr_rel1 = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_rel1_munts_fac when t.tr_rel2 = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_rel2_munts_fac when t.tr_vruchtrelatie = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_vruchtrek_mnt_fac else 1 end as clientaccountfactor, case when t.tr_rel1 = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_rel1_munts_rcp when t.tr_rel2 = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_rel2_munts_rcp when t.tr_vruchtrelatie = ppr.ppr_relatienummer then t.tr_vruchtrek_mnt_rcp else 1 end as clientaccountreciproke, pmg.pmg_transdatum as peildatum, pmg.pmg_rekening_soort as rekeningsoort from positiemutaties_geld pmg, producten_per_relatie ppr, rekeningen_per_product rpp, transakties t where ppr.ppr_id = ~1 and rpp.rpp_relatienummer = ppr.ppr_relatienummer and rpp.rpp_productnummer = ppr.ppr_productnummer and rpp.rpp_volgnr_per_product = ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product and pmg.pmg_relatienr = rpp.rpp_relatienummer and pmg.pmg_rekening_soort = rpp.rpp_rekeningsoort and pmg.pmg_rekeningnr = rpp.rpp_rekening_nummer and pmg.pmg_rekening_munts = rpp.rpp_valuta and pmg.pmg_tr_volgnummer = t.tr_volgnummer and t.tr_indicatie in (select distinct (pct.pct_transactiesoort) from performance_cat_trans pct inner join performance_calc_cat pcc on pct.pct_perf_calc_cat = pcc.pcc_perf_calc_cat inner join performance_rap_koppeling prk on pct.pct_perf_calc_cat = prk.prk_perf_calc_cat where prk.prk_perf_rap_cat in (~2, ~3, ~4, ~5, ~6) and pcc.pcc_rendement_corr = 1) and t.tr_herkomst_code_tr not in(~7,~8) and pmg.pmg_transdatum between ~9 and ~10
UNION ALL
select t.tr_indicatie as indication, t.tr_herkomst_code_tr as origincode, t.tr_mutatiecode as mutationcode, t.tr_mut_gemaakt as mutationmade, t.tr_transdatum as transactiondate, round(pom.pom_mutatie_aantal * pom.pom_mutatie_prijsbe * t.tr_prijs_factor,4) as amountbe, round(pom.pom_mutatie_aantal * pom.pom_mutatie_prijscl * t.tr_prijs_factor,4) as amountcl, 0 as clientquote, 0 as clientfactor, 0 as clientreciproke, ' ' as clientaccountcurrency, 0 as clientaccountquote, 0 as clientaccountfactor, 0 as clientaccountreciproke, pom.pom_peildatum as peildatum, pom.pom_rekening_soort from posmuttransdatum pom, producten_per_relatie ppr, rekeningen_per_product rpp, transakties t, beleggingsinstrument b where ppr.ppr_id = ~1 and rpp.rpp_relatienummer = ppr.ppr_relatienummer and rpp.rpp_productnummer = ppr.ppr_productnummer and rpp.rpp_volgnr_per_product = ppr.ppr_volgnr_per_product and pom.pom_relatienr = rpp.rpp_relatienummer and pom.pom_rekening_soort = rpp.rpp_rekeningsoort and pom.pom_rekeningnr = rpp.rpp_rekening_nummer and pom.pom_symbool = b.be_symbool and pom.pom_optietype = b.be_optietype and pom.pom_expiratiedatum = b.be_expiratiedatum and pom.pom_exerciseprijs = b.be_exerciseprijs and pom.pom_tr_volgnummer = t.tr_volgnummer and t.tr_indicatie in (select distinct (pct.pct_transactiesoort) from performance_cat_trans pct inner join performance_calc_cat pcc on pct.pct_perf_calc_cat = pcc.pcc_perf_calc_cat inner join performance_rap_koppeling prk on pct.pct_perf_calc_cat = prk.prk_perf_calc_cat where prk.prk_perf_rap_cat in (~2, ~3, ~4, ~5, ~6) and pcc.pcc_rendement_corr = 1) and t.tr_herkomst_code_tr not in(~7,~8) and pom.pom_peildatum between ~9 and ~10)X where X.amountbe <> 0 order by X.transactiondate
